68: /**
69:  * Parse a JSONL file into an array of event objects.
70:  *
71:  * @param {string} filePath - Path to the JSONL file.
72:  * @returns {Array<Object>} Parsed event objects.
73:  * @throws {Error} If a line is malformed JSON or not an object.
