387: /**
388:  * CLI entry point. Parses arguments, reads the AI council state JSONL file,
389:  * derives a council graph payload, and either writes it to the runtime graph
390:  * or prints it in dry-run mode.
391:  *
392:  * @param {string[]} [argv] - CLI arguments (default: process.argv.slice(2)).
